        <p style="color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
         If you follow me on Twitter, you\xe2\x80\x99ve likely heard of Party Round. Every time Party Round launched a new drop, or really tweeted anything at all in the past two years since Not Boring Capital first invested, sure as night follows day, a DM popped into my Twitter inbox, demanding amplification.
        </p>
